If this option is true, comments included in SQL query are removed

If there is below query, comments are removed and saved.

    /* 12345abcde */ SELECT * FROM TABLE

After applied, query should be shown like below.

    SELECT * FROM TABLE


This option is used when the comment contains randomly generated code or string, and the they are not cached and all of the them are stored, which affects performance..

---

* Default : false
* Type : Boolean
* Restart : Not required
* Version supported : 5.4.3.2